               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="2" to="6r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1716Kidanz">Kidān za-nagh</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ኪዳን፡ ዘነግህ፡ ዘነገሮሙ፡ ለአበዊነ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡ ወበረከቶሙ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ አቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ ት<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ሣኤ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                     </incipit>
                     <note>
                        The text terminates with a blessing: <q xml:lang="gez">በቃለ፡ ኪዳንከ፡ 
                              <sic>አድኅኖሙ፡</sic>
                            ለአቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ ትንንሣኤ።</q>. 
                        The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName> is mentioned in the incipit of the text 
                        and in the concluding blessing. 
                        </note>
                  </msItem> 
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="6v" to="25r"/>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#SerataQeddase">Maṣḥafa qǝddāse, Śǝrʿāta qǝddāseሥርዓተ፡ ቅዳሴ፡</title>
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ሥርዓተ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ዘይደሉ፡ ከመ፡ ይበሉ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወዲያቆን፨ 
                        ወሕዝብ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ዘመፍትው፡ በበጊዜሁ፡ በከመ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ አበዊነ፡ ግብጻውያን፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem> 
                 
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="25r" to="83v"/>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3189Anapho">Fourteen Anaphoras</title>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.1">
                        <locus from="25r" to="34v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1104Anapho">Anaphora of the Apostles</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘአበዊነ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡ ወበረከቶሙ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ አቡነ፡ <del rend="effaced">ወልደ፡ ትንሣኤ።</del> ወ<del rend="expunctuated">ልደ፡</del> ምስለ፡ 
                           እኁነ፡ <add place="inline">ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡</add> 
                           <del rend="effaced">ዐተባ፡ ሊባኖስ፡</del> ወብእሲቱ፡ <add place="inline">ለተ፡ ስላሴ፡</add> 
                           <del rend="effaced">ላህየ፡ ድንግል።</del> ወአቡሆሙ፡ <add place="inline">ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</add> ግርማ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                        </incipit>
                        <note>
                           Several names are mentioned in the supplication formula at the beginning of the text. Some of them have been deleted or effaced: 
                           <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11589AtabaL">ʿAtabā Libānos</persName>, 
                           his wife <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11590LaheyaD">Lāhǝya Dǝngǝl</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11591GermaY">Gǝrmā Yoḥannǝs</persName>, 
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11592WaldaG">Walda Giyorgis</persName>. 
                           Other names have been written over the previous ones in a different hand: <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11593SebhatL">Sǝbḥat Laʾab</persName>, 
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11594WalattaS">Walatta Śǝllāse</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11595GabraK">Gabra Krǝstos</persName>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2">
                        <locus from="34v" to="39r"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">Anaphora of Our Lord Jesus Christ</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘእግዚእነ፡ ወአምላክነ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በረከቱ፡ ትኩን፡ ምስለ፡ አቡነ፡ <del>ወልደ፡ ትንሣኤ።</del> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                        </incipit>
                        <note> The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName> has been deleted from the supplication 
                           formula at the beginning of the text.</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.3">
                        <locus from="39r" to="51v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1099Anapho">Anaphora of Our Lady by Cyriacus of Behnesa</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ዘደረሰ፡ ላቲ፡ <del>በ</del>አባ፡ ህርያቆስ። ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ። ዘሀገረ፡ ብሕንሳ፨ ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ አቡነ፡ 
                           <del>ወልደ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ዐተባ፡ ሊባኖስ፡</del> 
                           <add place="inline">ስብሐት፡ 
                                 <sic>ለአበ፡</sic>
                              
                           </add> ለአለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                        </incipit>
                        <note>
                           The names of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11589AtabaL">ʿAtabā Libānos</persName> 
                           have been deleted in the supplication formula at the beginning of the text and replaced with that of 
                           <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11593SebhatL">Sǝbḥat Laʾab</persName>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.4">
                        <locus from="51v" to="55r"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3180Anapho">Anaphora by Dioscorus</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘድዮስ፡ ቆሮስ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ አመቱ፡ ላሕየ፡ ድንግል፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፨
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           ይዕቀብክሙ፡ በእንተ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ሥጋ፡ መለኮት፡ ወበእንተ፡ ደሙ፡ ደመ፡ ሕግ፡ ወሥርዓት። ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጸባዖት። ወወልደ፡ ማርያም፡ ስግው። ወበድንግልናሃ፡ ወበንጽሐ፡ 
                           ሥጋሃ፡ ሕትምት። ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                        </explicit>
                        <note>
                           The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11590LaheyaD">Lāhǝya Dǝngǝl</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the beginning of 
                           the text. Two names have been added in a secondary hand in the space before the title of the text: <q xml:lang="gez">ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡ ወውሉዱ፡ 
                              ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</q>, i.e. those of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11593SebhatL">Sǝbḥat Laʾab</persName> and his son 
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11595GabraK">Gabra Krǝstos</persName>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.5">
                        <locus from="55r" to="60v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3120Anapho">Anaphora by John Chrysostom</title>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           እግዚአብሔር፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ኵልክሙ። አሜን፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ይባርከነ፡ 
                              <sic>ወይሠሃለነ፨</sic>
                           
                        </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.6">
                        <locus from="60v" to="68v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1103Anapho">Anaphora of the 318 Fathers of Nicaea</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘ፫፻፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፨ ጸሎቶሙ፡ ወበረከቶሙ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ አቡነ፡ <del>ወልደ፡ ትንሣኤ፡</del> 
                           <add place="inline">ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡</add> ለዓለመ፡ 
                           ዓለም።
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           ዘተመጠውነ፡ በእደዊሆሙ፡ ዘንተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወልድከ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወደመ፡ መሲሕከ፡ ክቡር፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላክነ። አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ይረሲ፡ ይኩነነ፡ ለሕይወት፡ ወለመድኃኒት፨ ወለሥርየተ፡ ኃጢአት፨ 
                           አሜን፨
                        </explicit>
                        <note>The name of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName> has been deleted in the supplication formula at the 
                           beginning of the text and replaced with that of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11593SebhatL">Sǝbḥat Laʾab</persName>.</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.7">
                        <locus from="68v" to="74r"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2404Tanseu">Anaphora by Jacob of Serug</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘሥሩግ፨ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ እኁነ፡ <del>ዐተባ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ላሕየ፡</del> ድንግል፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፨ ፨ ተንሥኡ፡ በፍርሃተ፡ 
                           እግዚአብሔር፡ ከመ፡ ታጽምዑ፡ አርኅው፡ መሳክወ፡ አዕዛኒክሙ፡
                        </incipit>
                        <note>
                           The names of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11589AtabaL">ʿAtabā Libānos</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11590LaheyaD">Lāhǝya Dǝngǝl</persName> 
                           have been written and partly deleted from the supplication formula at the beginning of the text.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.8">
                        <locus from="74r" to="83v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1162Athana">Anaphora by Athanasius</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           አኰቲተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ አትናቴዎስ፡ በረከተ፡ አምላኩ፡ 
                              <sic>የሁሉ፡</sic>
                            ምስለ፡ አቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ <del>ትንሣኤ፡</del> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ዲ፨ 
                           ዮም፡ በዛቲ፡ ዕለት፡ እለ፡ ተጋዕክሙ፨ አጽምዑ፡ ቅዳሴሃ፡ ለሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ቅድስት፨
                        </incipit>
                        <note>
                           The name of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName> has been written in the supplication formula at the beginning 
                           of the text and partly erased.
                        </note>
                        <explicit type="subscriptio" xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#83v"/>
                        ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ወ<del>ልደ፡ ትንሣኤ፨</del> ዘወሀቦ፡ ለአቡነ፡ <del>ሊባኖስ፡</del> 
                           
                              <sic>ወይኵኖ፡</sic>
                            መርሃ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ 
                        ወጸሐፊሃ፡ አቡነ፡ <del>ወልደ፡ ማርያ<supplied reason="omitted">ም</supplied>፡</del> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን።
                        <note>
                           The note states that the book belonged to <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11588WaldaT">Walda Tǝnśāʾe</persName>, who gave it to 
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11589AtabaL">ʿAtabā Libānos</persName>. The note also indicates <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11596WaldaM">Walda Māryām</persName> 
                           as the scribe. All the three names have been partly or completely deleted.
                        </note>
                        </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                   </msItem>  
               </msContents>
          
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Codex">
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>
                           
